ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport how many plasma television screens have been purchased by his Department and its agencies, and at what cost, in the last 24 months.

reply.p: In the last 24 months, my Department has purchased one plasma television screen at a cost of £8,014.68 excluding VAT (£9,417.25 including VAT). The cost covered purchase and installation.
